1 STATE OF OKLAHOMA
2 2nd Session of the 60th Legislature (2026)
3 HOUSE BILL 3868 By: Gann
4
5
6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to cities and towns; enacting the
Cities and Towns Act of 2026; providing for
8 noncodification; and providing an effective date.
9
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
13 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
14 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Cities and
15 Towns Act of 2026".
16 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
